    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been so well-loved and is still in fantastic shape. It drives like a dream and is perfect for everything from your daily commute to fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s been super dependable for me, and I know you\u2019re going to love it just as much! Come take it for a spin!",
