    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis remains composed with recent subframe reinforcement and a refreshed VANOS system, addressing the platform's primary technical concerns. Suspension geometry is true, providing the communicative steering feel expected of this generation. While the exterior shows a light patina consistent with regular use, the powertrain and drivetrain are mechanically robust, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean interior and title. Reliable performance. No issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
